<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FERAS | DEV-MODE</title>
    <style>
        :root { --neon: #00f2ff; --bg: #0a0a0a; }
        body {
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .box {
            border: 1px solid var(--neon);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.2);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .box:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--neon); }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--neon);
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--neon);
        }
        .status {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #0f0;
        }
        .blink { animation: blink 1.5s infinite; }
        @keyframes blink { 0% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.3; } 100% { opacity: 1; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="box">
        <div class="status"><span class="blink">●</span> نظام التشغيل: TERMUX-ACTIVE</div>
        <h1>FERAS DEV</h1>
        <p>مرحباً بك في المنطقة البرمجية الخاصة بي.</p>
        <p style="color: #666;">تم الرفع بنجاح عبر GitHub CLI</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>



